This is the editable copy, only relevant cells can be modified:
 - Mouse over headings to see a description
 - Some fields use restricted values and will error if incorrect values entered (or drop-down not used)
 - Most drop-down lists have extended information in the 'ListData' worksheet.
 - See the 'Example' worksheet for examples.
 - Maximum of 100 files can be submitted in a manifest.
